{
  "stem": "24268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The irony of it, that this kind of tragedy, they were still asking for singing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think that's what gave them the hope, and they knew I was singing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's strange that people can-- I cannot bring up [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All I do is cry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that time I was giving, I think, giving strength to them to survive, obviously.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, I asked him if it's gonna be a transport to Daddy, to Markstadt, if he could help me to get to Daddy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, look, I cannot do whatever, they-- if I-- if it will be a transport, I will try.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So meantime, they called me, called the whole group, whoever was there, all the girls-- girls and women that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the SS came, and selected me because I tried to make myself small and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Meantime was even worse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't realize what I was doing to myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They probably send me to the worst in Bergen-Belsen, which that was a death camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought, as a child, if I'm gonna look delicate, maybe they will feel sorry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They will send me to a men's-- to where they always sent in the men's camp, that the girl works in the kitchen, has that ability more to survive, because she can eat better, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was-- you know, when you hear rumors, you just follow blindly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You never know which way really is right, and which is wrong.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I, that time, I-- and then when they selected me, the doctor said no.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did not understand why-- Darzitski, Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Darzitski.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For some reason maybe the Jews was-- knew that I was-- that I want to come to my daddy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He tried to take me out of this, and we did that three times.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
